            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "SE75v",
              "name": "articleBody",
              "width": 680,
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 36,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "fmDAu",
                  "fill": "#3D3D3D",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": 680,
                  "content": "物理学家说：物理是定律，其他都是建议。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.9,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 18,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "ExJ7c",
                  "fill": "#3D3D3D",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": 680,
                  "content": "在工程世界里，这句话意味着什么呢？",
                  "lineHeight": 1.9,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 17,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "s0iWx",
                  "fill": "#3D3D3D",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": 680,
                  "content": "第一性原理思维要求我们剥去所有的假设和惯例，回到问题的本质。不是别人怎么做，而是这件事本身的约束是什么。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.9,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 17,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "ylBwn",
                  "name": "quoteBlock",
                  "width": 680,
                  "fill": "#F5F0EA",
                  "cornerRadius": 4,
                  "stroke": {
                    "align": "inside",
                    "thickness": {
                      "left": 3
                    },
                    "fill": "#C4956A"
                  },
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 16,
                  "padding": [
                    28,
                    36
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "q2tAr",
                      "fill": "#6A6058",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 600,
                      "content": "最好的架构不是想出来的，而是在约束条件中生长出来的。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.8,
                      "fontFamily": "Playfair Display",
                      "fontSize": 17,
                      "fontWeight": "normal",
                      "fontStyle": "italic"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "1v4Py",
                  "fill": "#3D3D3D",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": 680,
                  "content": "当我们设计一个系统时，真正重要的是理解它的核心约束：",
                  "lineHeight": 1.9,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 17,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "fbmxd",
                  "name": "bulletList",
                  "width": 680,
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 8,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "tsFQr",
                      "fill": "#4A4540",
                      "content": "• 数据一致性要求是什么？",
                      "lineHeight": 1.6,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "7NKyJ",
                      "fill": "#4A4540",
                      "content": "• 性能瓶颈在哪里？",
                      "lineHeight": 1.6,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "aJd90",
                      "fill": "#4A4540",
                      "content": "• 团队的维护能力边界在哪里？",
                      "lineHeight": 1.6,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "Uw1PI",
                  "fill": "#3D3D3D",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": 680,
                  "content": "这些才是定律。其他的——框架选择、代码风格、部署方式——都只是建议。",
                  "lineHeight": 1.9,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 17,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "bdarw",
              "width": "fit_content(0)",
              "height": 120
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
